Hello Dear,

My name is Richard Clarke, your old friend. I am very happy to inform you
about my success in getting those funds transferred under the co-operation
of a new partner from JAPAN. Presently I am in JAPAN for investment
projects with my new partner. Meanwhile, I didn't forget your efforts and
attempts to assist me in getting the fund in the past despite that we
didn't succeed at the time. It was the will of God, but finally I succeeded
with the help of another partner.

In appreciation of your earlier assistance to me in receiving the fund, I
have decided to compensate you with the sum of $1,500,000.00 USD(One
Million Five Hundred Thousand United States Dollars). Please accept it as a
token of appreciation from me. Presently, I am in JAPAN for an investment
project. Since it was difficult to contact you before I traveled due to the
urgency of my business schedule, I have left instructions with my personal
secretary Mr. Raphael Johnson, Please contact him through his E-mail
address or phone number below.

Secretary Name: MR RAPHAEL JOHNSON
E-mail:  raphaeldzie@gmail.com

Please email him and inform him that I have contacted you and that he
should go ahead and release your compensation fund to you. Send the below
information to him for verification

Your Full Name:
Your Address:
Phone Number:
A Copy of Your ID:

Ask him to RELEASE the sum of $1.5million USD ATM CARD which I prepared and
kept for your compensation for all the past efforts and attempts to assist
me in this matter. I appreciate your efforts at that time very much. So
feel free and get in touch with Mr.Raphael Johnson. Please do let me know
immediately you receive it so that we can share our joy and happiness after
all the sufferings at that time.

At the moment, I am very busy here because of the investment projects which
me and my new partner are having at hand. Finally, remember that I had left
an instruction to MR RAPHAEL JOHNSON on your behalf to receive that fund.
Therefore feel free to get in touch with him and he will RELEASE the FUND
to you without delay.

Take care of yourself and bye for now, please don' t forget to contact me
when you are through with that, and please do not be worried if you did not
hear from me for sometime because i will be very busy and will not have
time to be checking this email always, thanks.

Yours Truly,
MR RICHARD CLARKE

